reviewText:
First off, this dvd is only a little over ten minutes long, so if you're purchasing it, make certain the price is less than $10 (shipping inlcuded)

The DVD consists of three 'music videos'; the single quotes indicate that the term is used loosely...as the videos are basically just footage of the 5 Browns playing their five pianos in a desert or an airplane hanger.

Videos feature the following songs:

1.  American Hymn Fantasy
2.  Rhapsody In Blue (George Gershwin)
3.  The Firebird (Igor Stravinsky)
